Description: Simple applicant tracking software
Full Description: SquareHire is a software as a service (SAAS) application that provides applicant tracking software to small businesses.   It's basically trying to be the BaseCamp of the applicant tracking space. The service launched in May 2011 as HireFlo, and later had an official public launch at the 2011 Intuit App Showcase.  It was one of the first apps offered through Intuit's App Store. The service is built around three key functions.   First is a jobs page. the system provides a company jobs page that can be displayed on customer websites via a javascript widget. Second is job distribution.  When companies enter jobs, those jobs are published to the free job board ecosystem through relationships with SimplyHired, GlassDoor, JuJu, and other networks. Third is applicant tracking.  The system provides a central online resume database that companies can use to rate and manage applicants.

Full Description: JUST BECAUSE YOUR GRANDFATHER DID IT THIS WAY FOR 50 YEARS, DOESN'T MEAN THAT'S HOW YOU HAVE TO DO IT. New Mousetrap! Half the installation time!! The Easy2Install switch and outlet system is the Professional and Do It Yourself solution. The system consists of combined face plate and switch or outlet units which include prewire connections to the switches by connector rail and standard terminal connection plugs. The Easy2Install electrical connection system is all incorporated into the faceplate, covered for safety and labeled for the easy install in minutes. Wiring a home or room with the Easy2Install unit is as easy as it gets for the beginners and professionals and most important you reduce install time. The faceplate Includes an easy peel off, paint mask. The system is manufactured of quality fire retardant materials and components, all standard to the industry. The pressure on electrical contractors today to be competitive and faster on the job with quicker completion dates is standard in the industry today. BJJ promotes the concept that a weaker person can successfully defend against a bigger, stronger, heavier assailant by using leverage.
Full Description: Memorial Brazilian Jiu Jitsu School, with the goal of spreading the love for Brazilian Jiu Jitsu (BJJ), has been successfully teaching this martial art the gentle way for the last five years. The head coach, Jackson Fortunato, had a vision of spreading his knowledge of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu among people of all ages. He began in London, UK after completing his Graduation in Physical Education. His BJJ school soon became one of the most successful BJJ schools in the UK. After successfully expanding the gentle art of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu around all of Europe, he planned to start a new journey and moved to Houston to give self defense classes in Houston. He opened The Memorial Brazilian Jiu Jitsu School along with Jose Henrique Leao Teixeira Filho (Master), and Rafael Castillo (Manager). The love of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu is common among these three. Memorial BJJ School runs 4 training programs and self defense classes in Houston that focus on people of different age groups Future Champ Program is for kids between 5-8 years of age Kids at this age learn BJJ Houston in a playful way at the school. The games and activities are specially designed for kids at this Houston Jiu Jitsu school so that they learn while they play. Juniors Empowered Program is for children between 9-13 years of age Cases of bullying are rising and children of this age group are more prone to bullying that's why they need the self defense classes in Houston. These classes teach them about self-defense techniques they can use in the case they are attacked. BJJ isn't a violent art, it's a gentle art and children of this age need this art so that they can control the situation which involves ground fights. Adult Fundamental Program is for Adults People with no prior experience in any form of martial arts can also join this program and start learning the basic Brazilian Jiu Jitsu techniques. After the completion of the session, you can earn BJJ Blue Belt. Women's Empowerment Class is specially designed for Women The specially designed program for women teaches them to defend the 15 most common attacks. Brazilian Jiu Jitsu is a skill-based art. You can improve your skills even if you are a weaker, smaller or thinner person. Memorial Brazilian Jiu Jitsu School is making the people ready to defeat their attackers without using the kicks and punches. This is already becoming popular than other Jiu Jitsu schools in the region. And, people are enjoying learning BJJ Houston Tx from the experts at the Memorial Brazilian Jiu Jitsu School. The school offers the first class free of cost and if you like the experience, you can signup for a 10-day free trial as well.
